---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import CTASection from '../components/CTASection.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Metodología"
  description="Descubre la metodología educativa del Instituto Online Osbord. Formación 100% online, tutorías personalizadas y aprendizaje basado en proyectos reales."
>
  <Header />
  <main>
    <section id="metodologia" class="bg-brand-navy py-20 lg:py-24 text-white relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-navy to-brand-navy-light"></div>
      <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <nav class="mb-8" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
          <ol class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-gray-400">
            <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-brand-gold transition-colors">Inicio</a></li>
            <li>/</li>
            <li class="text-brand-gold font-semibold">Metodología</li>
          </ol>
        </nav>
        <div class="max-w-3xl space-y-6 animate-fade-in-up">
          <span class="section-label">Cómo Enseñamos</span>
          <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white leading-[1.08] tracking-tight">
            Metodología de <span class="text-brand-gold">Alto Rendimiento</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
            Un modelo educativo diseñado para profesionales que no pueden parar. Aprende a tu ritmo, con el acompañamiento de expertos activos en la industria.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 space-y-20">
        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-brand-gold/10 rounded-brand-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-brand-gold font-extrabold text-xl" style="font-family: var(--font-montserrat);">01</span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight">Campus Virtual 24/7</h2>
            <div class="gold-divider"></div>
            <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed text-lg">Accede a todo tu contenido académico desde cualquier dispositivo, en cualquier momento. Nuestro campus virtual está diseñado para una experiencia de aprendizaje fluida e intuitiva.</p>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-600">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 0 1 .143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 0 1 1.05-.143Z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                Acceso de por vida al material del curso
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-600">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 0 1 .143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 0 1 1.05-.143Z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                Compatible con móvil, tablet y desktop
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-600">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 0 1 .143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 0 1 1.05-.143Z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                Contenido en vídeo HD y recursos descargables
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-neutral rounded-brand-xl p-12 border border-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center min-h-[300px]">
            <div class="text-center space-y-4">
              <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto bg-brand-gold/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-brand-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 17.25v1.007a3 3 0 0 1-.879 2.122L7.5 21h9l-.621-.621A3 3 0 0 1 15 18.257V17.25m6-12V15a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25 2.25H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 3 15V5.25m18 0A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 18.75 3H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 3 5.25m18 0V12a2.25 2.25 0 0 1-2.25 2.25H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 1 3 12V5.25"/></svg>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Plataforma de Aprendizaje</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
          <div class="order-2 lg:order-1 bg-brand-neutral rounded-brand-xl p-12 border border-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center min-h-[300px]">
            <div class="text-center space-y-4">
              <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto bg-brand-gold/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-brand-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M18 18.72a9.094 9.094 0 0 0 3.741-.479 3 3 0 0 0-4.682-2.72m.94 3.198.001.031c0 .225-.012.447-.037.666A11.944 11.944 0 0 1 12 21c-2.17 0-4.207-.576-5.963-1.584A6.062 6.062 0 0 1 6 18.719m12 0a5.971 5.971 0 0 0-.941-3.197m0 0A5.995 5.995 0 0 0 12 12.75a5.995 5.995 0 0 0-5.058 2.772m0 0a3 3 0 0 0-4.681 2.72 8.986 8.986 0 0 0 3.74.477m.94-3.197a5.971 5.971 0 0 0-.94 3.197M15 6.75a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Zm6 3a2.25 2.25 0 1 1-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 0 1 4.5 0Zm-13.5 0a2.25 2.25 0 1 1-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 0 1 4.5 0Z"/></svg>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Mentoría Personalizada</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="order-1 lg:order-2 space-y-6">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-brand-gold/10 rounded-brand-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-brand-gold font-extrabold text-xl" style="font-family: var(--font-montserrat);">02</span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight">Tutoría Personalizada</h2>
            <div class="gold-divider"></div>
            <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed text-lg">Cada alumno tiene asignado un tutor especializado que acompaña su progreso, resuelve dudas y proporciona feedback continuo en cada módulo.</p>
            <ul class="space-y-3">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-600">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 0 1 .143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 0 1 1.05-.143Z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                Respuesta en menos de 24 horas
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-600">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 0 1 .143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 0 1 1.05-.143Z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                Sesiones 1:1 opcionales por videollamada
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-gray-600">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-gold flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.704 4.153a.75.75 0 0 1 .143 1.052l-8 10.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.127.075l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06-1.06l3.894 3.893 7.48-9.817a.75.75 0 0 1 1.05-.143Z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
                Corrección detallada de proyectos
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-brand-gold/10 rounded-brand-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-brand-gold font-extrabold text-xl" style="font-family: var(--font-montserrat);">03</span>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight">Proyecto Final + Certificación</h2>
            <div class="gold-divider"></div>
            <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed text-lg">Al concluir tu máster, desarrollas un proyecto profesional real que defiendes ante un comité académico. Tras su aprobación, recibes tu diploma con posibilidad de apostilla internacional.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-neutral rounded-brand-xl p-12 border border-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center min-h-[300px]">
            <div class="text-center space-y-4">
              <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto bg-brand-gold/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-brand-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M4.26 10.147a60.438 60.438 0 0 0-.491 6.347A48.62 48.62 0 0 1 12 20.904a48.62 48.62 0 0 1 8.232-4.41 60.46 60.46 0 0 0-.491-6.347m-15.482 0a50.636 50.636 0 0 0-2.658-.813A59.906 59.906 0 0 1 12 3.493a59.903 59.903 0 0 1 10.399 5.84c-.896.248-1.783.52-2.658.814m-15.482 0A50.717 50.717 0 0 1 12 13.489a50.702 50.702 0 0 1 7.74-3.342"/></svg>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Diploma Apostillado</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <CTASection headline="¿Listo para empezar?" subtext="Solicita información sobre nuestros programas y descubre cuál es el más adecuado para tu perfil profesional." buttonText="SOLICITAR INFORMACIÓN" />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
